00:14:49.270 --> 00:14:49.670
Hello.

00:14:49.790 --> 00:14:50.240
Hello.

00:14:50.290 --> 00:14:51.220
Narcotics Unit.

00:14:51.390 --> 00:14:52.920
Here's the search warrant.

00:15:03.830 --> 00:15:04.640
What's this?

00:15:06.400 --> 00:15:07.120
And this?

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:20.720
You're back.

00:15:23.320 --> 00:15:25.540
How was your chat with your cop friends?

00:15:26.670 --> 00:15:27.330
It was fine.

00:15:27.550 --> 00:15:29.010
Just eating and drinking.

00:15:29.740 --> 00:15:30.910
Nothing special.

00:15:34.630 --> 00:15:36.560
Since when do you play video games?

00:15:36.910 --> 00:15:38.120
I'm not playing.

00:15:38.790 --> 00:15:39.510
I meet them

00:15:39.510 --> 00:15:41.150
in this game and communicate

00:15:41.440 --> 00:15:42.510
using code words.

00:15:43.440 --> 00:15:44.080
Look.

00:15:44.510 --> 00:15:45.170
This guy...

00:15:46.150 --> 00:15:47.010
is called Quan.

00:15:51.320 --> 00:15:52.580
I set up a meet with Quan

00:15:52.610 --> 00:15:53.810
in four days.

00:15:54.160 --> 00:15:55.290
I also booked a boat.

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:57.080
If he turns on me,

00:15:57.080 --> 00:15:58.030
I'll kill him,

00:15:58.030 --> 00:15:59.120
take his money,

00:16:00.510 --> 00:16:01.830
and set sail immediately.

00:16:01.830 --> 00:16:03.630
He must have made a lot recently.

00:16:04.210 --> 00:16:06.270
Enough for us to live it up for a while.

00:16:15.710 --> 00:16:16.920
We're leaving

00:16:17.160 --> 00:16:18.070
in four days?

00:16:18.670 --> 00:16:19.640
That soon?

00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:22.390
I said "if."

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:25.040
But knowing Quan,

00:16:25.720 --> 00:16:26.960
I'm 80% sure

00:16:26.960 --> 00:16:29.420
I can convince him to work with me.

00:16:30.300 --> 00:16:31.140
In that case,

00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:32.430
we can stay in Nuanhai

00:16:32.430 --> 00:16:33.550
for a while longer.

00:16:34.590 --> 00:16:35.590
What if he

00:16:36.510 --> 00:16:38.120
put all the money in the bank?

00:16:38.650 --> 00:16:39.780
We are drug dealers.

00:16:40.420 --> 00:16:42.610
Why would we put money in a bank?

00:16:47.870 --> 00:16:49.440
I'm not ready to go abroad.

00:16:51.590 --> 00:16:53.080
You don't have to go.

00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:55.270
When you get caught,

00:16:55.710 --> 00:16:57.070
I'll pray for you

00:16:57.100 --> 00:16:58.500
at Wat Pho.

00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:10.960
I fixed it for you.

00:17:11.950 --> 00:17:12.869
I can't believe

00:17:12.910 --> 00:17:14.710
you kept a cheap 200-yuan gadget

00:17:14.869 --> 00:17:16.180
for so many years.

00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:31.810
It's ugly.

00:17:39.790 --> 00:17:40.640
Is it?

00:17:48.650 --> 00:17:53.970
[Nuanfeng Hengke Electronics Co., Ltd.]

00:18:03.340 --> 00:18:04.140
Cheng Ken.

00:18:04.750 --> 00:18:05.510
Get in.

00:18:19.840 --> 00:18:20.880
We've met before.

00:18:21.590 --> 00:18:22.790
You probably forgot.

00:18:27.110 --> 00:18:27.790
Really?

00:18:29.160 --> 00:18:30.350
There are too many people at the factory.

00:18:30.350 --> 00:18:31.350
I don't remember.

00:18:33.790 --> 00:18:34.920
Our factory is huge.

00:18:35.420 --> 00:18:38.150
Many families depend on it
for their livelihood.

00:18:39.100 --> 00:18:40.690
Some work honestly.

00:18:41.750 --> 00:18:43.000
And some are like us,

00:18:43.390 --> 00:18:44.720
using certain methods.

00:18:45.160 --> 00:18:46.960
Everyone uses their own skills.

00:18:47.400 --> 00:18:48.860
So you need to understand,

00:18:49.730 --> 00:18:51.060
we're not acting alone.

00:18:51.670 --> 00:18:53.130
And what we're discussing

00:18:53.680 --> 00:18:55.740
isn't just about one or two invoices.

00:18:57.040 --> 00:18:59.280
That's exactly why I came to you.

00:19:01.360 --> 00:19:03.950
I'm not here to cut off anyone's income.

00:19:05.980 --> 00:19:06.720
I...

00:19:07.100 --> 00:19:08.000
I just want...

00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:09.330
To get a piece of the pie?

00:19:15.510 --> 00:19:16.640
I don't know if Mr. Sun

00:19:16.640 --> 00:19:18.240
told you about my situation.

00:19:20.070 --> 00:19:22.310
My parents are gone. My wife too.

00:19:22.710 --> 00:19:24.990
It's just me and my daughter now.

00:19:25.460 --> 00:19:26.790
My daughter has uremia.

00:19:27.900 --> 00:19:29.230
I need money to save her.

00:19:30.030 --> 00:19:31.790
I make 3,800 a month.

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:32.740
It's not enough.

00:19:32.740 --> 00:19:34.590
What's that got to do with me?

00:19:36.100 --> 00:19:37.050
And why should I?

00:19:38.170 --> 00:19:40.700
Just because you're
the factory accountant?

00:19:40.800 --> 00:19:43.730
Wouldn't it be easier for me
to go straight to Mr. Sun?

00:19:54.440 --> 00:19:55.750
Sure, that would work.

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:58.360
But the premise is...

00:19:59.800 --> 00:20:00.860
no one reports you.

00:20:06.320 --> 00:20:07.720
Are you blackmailing me?

00:20:24.590 --> 00:20:25.920
Ever been to this river?

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:27.080
No.

00:20:29.160 --> 00:20:30.270
Believe it or not,

00:20:31.210 --> 00:20:33.010
I'll throw you in right now.

00:20:36.040 --> 00:20:36.930
I believe you.

00:20:38.740 --> 00:20:40.630
But when I got in your car just now,

00:20:41.650 --> 00:20:43.090
the factory cameras

00:20:43.120 --> 00:20:44.250
probably caught it.

00:20:45.270 --> 00:20:46.550
If I drown,

00:20:47.100 --> 00:20:48.360
you pay with your life.

00:20:49.270 --> 00:20:51.030
If I half-drown, you pay cash.

00:21:00.160 --> 00:21:01.890
You really are going for broke.

00:21:03.630 --> 00:21:04.310
Fine.

00:21:06.330 --> 00:21:07.760
I underestimated you.

00:21:30.190 --> 00:21:30.990
12,000.

00:21:31.430 --> 00:21:32.290
Is that enough?

00:21:36.070 --> 00:21:38.200
I'll pay you 12,000 a month from now on.

00:21:38.650 --> 00:21:39.610
I don't need

00:21:40.420 --> 00:21:41.460
to teach you what to do, right?

00:21:41.460 --> 00:21:42.090
No need.

00:21:42.830 --> 00:21:43.630
I'm a pro.

00:22:28.340 --> 00:22:30.270
Pleasure doing business with you.

00:22:48.820 --> 00:22:50.190
Regarding this case,

00:22:50.250 --> 00:22:50.720
[Nuan'an Pharmacy Illegal Prescription
Drug Sales Case Press Conference]

00:22:50.720 --> 00:22:52.120
we mobilized our forces.

00:22:52.310 --> 00:22:53.750
During the search,

00:22:54.040 --> 00:22:56.590
we discovered
a large cache of illegal drugs hidden

00:22:56.590 --> 00:22:57.910
inside the Nuan'an Pharmacy on Haiyi Road.

00:22:57.910 --> 00:22:58.720
[Nuanfeng Narcotics]

00:22:58.720 --> 00:22:59.350
Our bureau

00:22:59.630 --> 00:23:01.360
immediately set up a task force

00:23:01.400 --> 00:23:03.330
to carry out a full investigation.

00:23:04.160 --> 00:23:05.400
We have since confirmed

00:23:05.400 --> 00:23:07.440
that multiple licensed

00:23:08.170 --> 00:23:10.430
physicians are implicated in this case,

00:23:10.550 --> 00:23:13.750
illegally promoting
smuggled medications to patients.

00:23:14.240 --> 00:23:15.300
Yang Xinyu, right?

00:23:15.360 --> 00:23:16.960
We're with the County Narcotics Unit.

00:23:16.960 --> 00:23:18.410
You're being summoned according to law.

00:23:18.410 --> 00:23:19.540
Here is the summons.

00:23:19.620 --> 00:23:20.380
Come with us.

00:23:23.660 --> 00:23:24.460
Currently,

00:23:25.010 --> 00:23:26.540
the owner of Nuan'an Pharmacy, Mr. Li,

00:23:26.540 --> 00:23:26.970
[Nuan'an Pharmacy Illegal Prescription
Drug Sales Case Press Conference]

00:23:26.970 --> 00:23:28.250
has been legally

00:23:28.650 --> 00:23:30.650
taken into criminal custody.

00:23:31.410 --> 00:23:32.940
We have both the confidence

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:33.960
and the resolve

00:23:34.160 --> 00:23:35.080
to investigate this case

00:23:35.080 --> 00:23:35.920
to the very end

00:23:36.400 --> 00:23:38.530
and restore safety to this community.

00:23:41.000 --> 00:23:42.590
None of the illegal meds from

00:23:42.590 --> 00:23:43.350
that pharmacy

00:23:43.350 --> 00:23:45.550
match what Liu Qiang and Tang Sile took.

00:23:45.790 --> 00:23:47.070
The bar and Yu Qing's place

00:23:47.070 --> 00:23:48.400
came up clean.

00:23:48.850 --> 00:23:51.510
Nothing suspicious
at Wang Ping's house either.

00:23:51.510 --> 00:23:52.200
Wenjing,

00:23:52.220 --> 00:23:54.020
your intuition's rarely wrong.

00:23:54.240 --> 00:23:56.030
Did you check
the surveillance near the bar?

00:23:56.030 --> 00:23:56.640
Yes.

00:23:56.750 --> 00:23:57.440
Well,

00:23:57.510 --> 00:23:59.190
there's only one camera
at a nearby intersection.

00:23:59.190 --> 00:24:01.240
It only shows Tang Sile
passing back and forth.

00:24:01.240 --> 00:24:02.260
Nothing else at all.

00:24:02.260 --> 00:24:03.670
Just one camera?

00:24:04.030 --> 00:24:06.430
You know the camera coverage
in our county.

00:24:07.440 --> 00:24:09.510
I have to say,
this guy is really something.

00:24:09.510 --> 00:24:10.310
He had the guts to kill himself,

00:24:10.310 --> 00:24:11.440
but not to face the law.

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:13.440
Now that he's dead, the lead is gone.

00:24:16.710 --> 00:24:17.350
He probably

00:24:17.350 --> 00:24:18.400
didn't even know

00:24:18.520 --> 00:24:19.750
he was gonna die today.

00:24:19.750 --> 00:24:20.240
Really?

00:24:23.070 --> 00:24:23.680
Maybe.

00:24:25.960 --> 00:24:27.030
Where are you going?

00:24:27.030 --> 00:24:28.160
Out. To find leads.

00:24:28.380 --> 00:24:29.000
Anyway,

00:24:29.000 --> 00:24:30.800
it beats guessing blindly here.

00:24:32.350 --> 00:24:33.850
He said you were guessing blindly.

00:24:33.850 --> 00:24:34.750
Let him talk.

00:24:34.750 --> 00:24:36.230
He can say whatever he wants.

00:24:36.230 --> 00:24:37.250
He's being sarcastic.

00:24:37.250 --> 00:24:39.050
I have to go to that rehab center.

00:24:39.630 --> 00:24:40.480
Do you want me to go with you?

00:24:40.480 --> 00:24:41.270
No need.

00:25:10.830 --> 00:25:11.640
Ken.

00:25:15.830 --> 00:25:16.560
Officer Jin,

00:25:16.780 --> 00:25:17.970
what brings you here?

00:25:17.970 --> 00:25:19.390
I arrested you the other day.

00:25:19.390 --> 00:25:20.210
It was a misunderstanding.

00:25:20.210 --> 00:25:21.770
So I came to apologize.

00:25:22.180 --> 00:25:23.240
You must be joking.

00:25:23.440 --> 00:25:25.000
You work for the government.

00:25:25.000 --> 00:25:27.400
How can you apologize
to common folks like us?

00:25:27.400 --> 00:25:28.550
Listen to you.

00:25:28.550 --> 00:25:29.000
You still...

00:25:29.000 --> 00:25:30.030
have a grudge against us.

00:25:30.030 --> 00:25:31.030
Then I didn't come for nothing.

00:25:31.030 --> 00:25:31.790
No grudge.

00:25:32.230 --> 00:25:33.750
Really, no grudge at all.

00:25:33.940 --> 00:25:35.410
You said it was a misunderstanding.

00:25:35.410 --> 00:25:36.610
Let's just let it go.

00:25:37.350 --> 00:25:38.480
Well, first time strangers,

00:25:38.480 --> 00:25:39.510
second time acquaintances, right?

00:25:39.510 --> 00:25:40.190
It's good.

00:25:40.720 --> 00:25:41.400
I...

00:25:42.000 --> 00:25:43.270
I've got stuff today.

00:25:43.270 --> 00:25:44.160
Let's talk some other time.

00:25:44.160 --> 00:25:44.960
I'll see you out.

00:25:44.960 --> 00:25:46.030
What is it?

00:25:46.480 --> 00:25:47.110
I...

00:25:47.270 --> 00:25:48.070
I have to take

00:25:48.070 --> 00:25:49.200
the kid out later.

00:25:49.200 --> 00:25:50.750
I came just to see the kid.

00:25:50.770 --> 00:25:51.640
The other day at the station,

00:25:51.640 --> 00:25:53.440
you mentioned your family situation.

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:54.770
Your daughter is called...

00:25:54.770 --> 00:25:55.230
Jiajia.

00:25:55.240 --> 00:25:55.830
Jiajia.

00:25:55.830 --> 00:25:57.030
Right? I remember it.

00:25:57.080 --> 00:25:58.680
These fruits are for Jiajia.

00:25:59.330 --> 00:26:01.170
When I heard what you're going through,

00:26:01.170 --> 00:26:02.230
it really moved me.

00:26:02.340 --> 00:26:03.050
Really.

00:26:03.080 --> 00:26:04.350
You've had it so tough.

00:26:04.920 --> 00:26:05.830
I'm used to it.

00:26:05.920 --> 00:26:06.680
It's fine.

00:26:07.480 --> 00:26:08.680
Another time. You're busy too.

00:26:08.680 --> 00:26:09.200
Let's just...

00:26:09.200 --> 00:26:10.350
No, I'll just see the kid.

00:26:10.350 --> 00:26:12.280
I'll leave right after seeing her.

00:26:19.420 --> 00:26:20.100
Now's not

00:26:20.620 --> 00:26:21.730
really a good time.

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:23.280
Why not?

00:26:23.350 --> 00:26:23.880
Well,

00:26:23.880 --> 00:26:25.200
I'll just see the kid and leave.

00:26:25.200 --> 00:26:26.240
It's not that it's inconvenient at home.

00:26:26.240 --> 00:26:26.970
It's just...

00:26:27.110 --> 00:26:28.200
we have an appointment.

00:26:28.200 --> 00:26:29.160
I'll go up and get her,

00:26:29.160 --> 00:26:30.820
then take her to the hospital.

00:26:31.680 --> 00:26:32.590
That's perfect.

00:26:32.590 --> 00:26:33.720
I'm heading back to the station.
It's on the way.

00:26:33.720 --> 00:26:34.920
You can give me a ride.

00:26:35.270 --> 00:26:36.720
Your station is quite

00:26:36.720 --> 00:26:37.830
far from the hospital.

00:26:37.830 --> 00:26:38.550
It's not that far.

00:26:38.550 --> 00:26:39.160
I'll walk from there.

00:26:39.160 --> 00:26:40.420
Consider it exercise.

00:26:40.950 --> 00:26:41.880
Look,

00:26:42.000 --> 00:26:43.720
I took time off work and bought fruit.

00:26:43.720 --> 00:26:45.110
You wouldn't mind
giving me a lift, would you?

00:26:45.110 --> 00:26:46.070
No.

00:26:47.050 --> 00:26:47.980
I wouldn't mind.

00:26:50.030 --> 00:26:50.240
Tell you what.

00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:50.550
I...

00:26:50.550 --> 00:26:51.070
Fine.

00:26:51.160 --> 00:26:51.680
I...

00:26:51.720 --> 00:26:53.160
I'll go up, get the kid,
and come right down.

00:26:53.160 --> 00:26:53.480
Okay?

00:26:53.480 --> 00:26:53.790
It's fine.

00:26:53.790 --> 00:26:54.920
I'll go up with you.

00:26:55.200 --> 00:26:56.510
I'll be right back down.

00:26:56.510 --> 00:26:57.240
I want to see where you live,

00:26:57.240 --> 00:26:58.640
so I can visit more often.

00:27:01.660 --> 00:27:02.190
Alright.

00:27:02.490 --> 00:27:03.580
Might as well.

00:27:03.640 --> 00:27:04.070
Right?

00:27:04.120 --> 00:27:04.590
Let me do it.

00:27:04.590 --> 00:27:05.160
It's fine.

00:27:05.160 --> 00:27:06.440
I got it.

00:27:06.440 --> 00:27:07.240
Go ahead.

00:27:32.470 --> 00:27:33.190
Jiajia!

00:27:34.200 --> 00:27:34.920
Jiajia.

00:27:35.310 --> 00:27:35.910
Come here.

00:27:36.270 --> 00:27:36.880
Dad!

00:27:36.900 --> 00:27:37.310
Hurry.

00:27:37.310 --> 00:27:38.200
Change your shoes.
We're going to the hospital.

00:27:38.200 --> 00:27:39.330
We're running late.

00:27:40.750 --> 00:27:42.590
Dad, who is he?

00:27:42.920 --> 00:27:43.590
This is Uncle Jin.

00:27:43.590 --> 00:27:44.440
He's a police officer.

00:27:44.440 --> 00:27:45.310
Say hello to Uncle Jin.

00:27:45.310 --> 00:27:46.350
Hello, Uncle Jin.

00:27:46.350 --> 00:27:47.210
Hello, Jiajia.

00:27:47.210 --> 00:27:48.270
I'll go get the bag.

00:27:49.920 --> 00:27:50.920
I'll get it.

00:28:01.280 --> 00:28:02.540
Are you done changing?

00:28:02.910 --> 00:28:03.640
Officer Jin,

00:28:04.390 --> 00:28:06.520
just put the fruit on the coffee table.

00:28:07.830 --> 00:28:08.310
Okay.

00:28:08.400 --> 00:28:09.350
Let's go. Hurry.

00:28:09.350 --> 00:28:09.880
We don't have much time.

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:10.350
I put it here.

00:28:10.350 --> 00:28:10.880
Okay.

00:28:11.070 --> 00:28:11.960
Thanks.

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:13.240
What about this?

00:28:13.240 --> 00:28:14.250
I'll deal with it when I get back.

00:28:14.250 --> 00:28:14.860
Thank you.

00:28:17.860 --> 00:28:19.120
Let's go, Officer Jin.

00:28:21.410 --> 00:28:22.470
Slow down, Jiajia.

00:28:34.130 --> 00:28:34.920
Jiajia,

00:28:35.420 --> 00:28:37.950
doesn't your dad work hard
taking care of you?

00:28:38.530 --> 00:28:41.640
Dad gets up in the morning
to make me breakfast,

00:28:41.930 --> 00:28:43.240
then he goes to work.

00:28:43.590 --> 00:28:45.630
At night, he makes me dinner,

00:28:46.170 --> 00:28:47.130
plays with me,

00:28:47.510 --> 00:28:49.000
tells me stories,

00:28:49.240 --> 00:28:50.440
puts me to sleep.

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:52.880
And he takes me to the hospital a lot.

00:28:53.070 --> 00:28:54.200
Then your dad

00:28:54.200 --> 00:28:56.200
doesn't have any time to rest at all?

00:28:57.670 --> 00:28:59.360
If I wasn't sick,

00:28:59.420 --> 00:29:02.230
Dad wouldn't have to work so hard.

00:29:03.970 --> 00:29:05.030
It's okay, Jiajia.

00:29:06.040 --> 00:29:06.930
You

00:29:07.090 --> 00:29:08.330
will get better soon.

00:29:11.500 --> 00:29:13.240
I don't know much about this.

00:29:13.270 --> 00:29:16.000
Is the local hospital
capable of doing a kidney transplant?

00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:16.810
Yes.

00:29:17.300 --> 00:29:19.630
I'm seeing Director Song at the hospital.

00:29:19.840 --> 00:29:21.440
He is an expert in this field,

00:29:21.460 --> 00:29:22.260
an authority.

00:29:22.790 --> 00:29:24.200
He said he's confident

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:25.540
about the surgery.

00:29:25.720 --> 00:29:27.070
It's not that difficult.

00:29:27.070 --> 00:29:27.730
I trust him.

00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:31.120
What about the money?

00:29:31.420 --> 00:29:32.060
The cost.

00:29:33.590 --> 00:29:34.430
I know.

00:29:35.640 --> 00:29:37.310
The surgery costs 200,000.

00:29:37.640 --> 00:29:39.480
The medication after surgery

00:29:39.880 --> 00:29:40.720
and nutritional supplements

